1
00:01:37,840 --> 00:01:41,020
[The Epoch of Miyu]

2
00:01:41,130 --> 00:01:43,960
[Episode 21]

3
00:01:51,310 --> 00:01:52,910
Mr. Ji, you didn't call me out

4
00:01:53,310 --> 00:01:54,310
just to accompany you

5
00:01:54,310 --> 00:01:55,840
to pick up a teacup, did you?

6
00:01:57,280 --> 00:01:58,479
You gave me the tea.

7
00:01:58,479 --> 00:01:59,759
So it's only right to ask your opinion

8
00:01:59,759 --> 00:02:00,920
on what kind of teacup

9
00:02:00,920 --> 00:02:01,980
would be suitable.

10
00:02:03,850 --> 00:02:04,630
By the way,

11
00:02:05,280 --> 00:02:06,350
how's your hand

12
00:02:06,350 --> 00:02:07,920
doing after earlier today?

13
00:02:09,280 --> 00:02:09,880
It's fine.

14
00:02:16,590 --> 00:02:17,190
It's fine.

15
00:02:19,390 --> 00:02:20,560
It's getting late.

16
00:02:21,840 --> 00:02:22,850
Just walk me this far.

17
00:02:22,850 --> 00:02:24,079
It's not much further ahead.

18
00:02:24,079 --> 00:02:25,240
-I can walk back by myself.
-It's okay.

19
00:02:25,240 --> 00:02:26,440
It's just a few steps.

20
00:02:26,710 --> 00:02:28,110
You really don't have to.

21
00:02:37,070 --> 00:02:38,630
What happened that night...

22
00:02:38,630 --> 00:02:39,690
It was an accident.

23
00:02:40,910 --> 00:02:41,710
Wasn't it?

24
00:02:44,030 --> 00:02:44,750
Yes,

25
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:46,680
it was an accident.

26
00:02:48,470 --> 00:02:49,680
And on top of that,

27
00:02:50,310 --> 00:02:51,560
I was running a fever.

28
00:02:51,579 --> 00:02:52,630
Could barely stand.

29
00:02:52,630 --> 00:02:53,910
So...

30
00:02:53,910 --> 00:02:55,310
I accidentally...

31
00:02:57,079 --> 00:02:58,740
I just want to say sorry to you.

32
00:02:58,750 --> 00:02:59,750
I caused you

33
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:01,030
too much trouble that night.

34
00:03:01,030 --> 00:03:01,910
It's fine.

35
00:03:03,790 --> 00:03:05,050
Let's forget about it.

36
00:03:10,470 --> 00:03:11,310
Okay.

37
00:03:12,750 --> 00:03:13,680
Let's forget it.

38
00:03:19,290 --> 00:03:20,470
It's getting late.

39
00:03:20,470 --> 00:03:21,680
I'll go back now.

40
00:03:22,030 --> 00:03:23,030
Get some rest.

41
00:03:23,210 --> 00:03:24,010
Okay.

42
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:25,190
Good night.

43
00:03:25,750 --> 00:03:26,470
Good night.

44
00:03:37,329 --> 00:03:39,140
♪ A flicker of dim light ♪

45
00:03:40,840 --> 00:03:42,480
♪ A bowl of warm soup ♪

46
00:03:41,310 --> 00:03:42,210
Miyu.

47
00:03:42,470 --> 00:03:43,670
Now, do you still want

48
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:45,910
to start a new relationship?

49
00:03:44,700 --> 00:03:46,610
♪ People in the city ♪

50
00:03:47,430 --> 00:03:50,370
♪ Squeezing into the hustle and bustle ♪

51
00:03:49,840 --> 00:03:51,079
Maybe it's because we've been through

52
00:03:51,079 --> 00:03:52,890
so much together at work.

53
00:03:52,300 --> 00:03:54,110
♪ The palms of time ♪

54
00:03:53,120 --> 00:03:54,560
Or maybe it's because he's helped me out

55
00:03:54,560 --> 00:03:56,230
so many times.

56
00:03:56,010 --> 00:03:59,150
♪ Grinding away the simple days ♪

57
00:03:56,700 --> 00:03:57,500
I admit.

58
00:03:58,120 --> 00:03:59,570
I have fallen

59
00:03:59,730 --> 00:04:00,450
for this man.

60
00:03:59,760 --> 00:04:02,680
♪ Sprinkling them into this busy world ♪

61
00:04:01,840 --> 00:04:02,520
In the past,

62
00:04:02,520 --> 00:04:03,560
I wouldn't have hesitated

63
00:04:03,560 --> 00:04:05,000
to see where it went.

64
00:04:03,680 --> 00:04:05,720
♪ To be tasted, bit by bit ♪

65
00:04:05,850 --> 00:04:06,890
But now?

66
00:04:07,200 --> 00:04:10,400
♪ Embracing this radiant world ♪

67
00:04:07,590 --> 00:04:08,680
I've just got out of

68
00:04:08,680 --> 00:04:09,860
a failed marriage

69
00:04:10,520 --> 00:04:11,650
and been back at work.

70
00:04:10,990 --> 00:04:14,020
♪ Keeps the heart from fading to grey ♪

71
00:04:11,960 --> 00:04:13,630
I still have a huge debt to pay.

72
00:04:13,950 --> 00:04:14,860
Love

73
00:04:14,610 --> 00:04:17,730
♪ Life's joy, sorrow, cold, and warmth ♪

74
00:04:15,310 --> 00:04:17,310
isn't going to be the cure to my life.

75
00:04:17,870 --> 00:04:21,160
[Purong Hotel Staff Apartment]

76
00:04:18,470 --> 00:04:20,950
♪ Intertwined within the mundane ♪

77
00:04:22,510 --> 00:04:25,820
♪ Let us bravely gather up ♪

78
00:04:26,370 --> 00:04:29,740
♪ The forgotten past ♪

79
00:04:30,720 --> 00:04:32,990
♪ There may be regrets ♪

80
00:04:34,650 --> 00:04:36,890
♪ There may be loneliness ♪

81
00:05:20,530 --> 00:05:23,540
[Charoro]

82
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:32,060
It doesn't matter.

83
00:05:33,750 --> 00:05:35,010
Let's forget about it.

84
00:05:41,510 --> 00:05:43,110
[Charoro]

85
00:05:43,330 --> 00:05:44,470
[Charoro]

86
00:05:49,930 --> 00:05:52,240
[Haven't been in touch for a while.
I guess you haven't changed your number.]

87
00:05:54,150 --> 00:05:56,180
[Haven't been in touch for a while.
I guess you haven't changed your number.]

88
00:05:54,270 --> 00:05:56,000
Haven't been in touch for a while.

89
00:05:56,000 --> 00:05:57,690
I guess you haven't changed your number.

90
00:05:56,210 --> 00:05:58,030
[I'm glad you're back.
Let's meet up sometime.]

91
00:05:58,060 --> 00:05:58,550
[Jiang Zhichun]

92
00:05:58,530 --> 00:06:00,140
I'm glad you're back.

93
00:06:00,480 --> 00:06:02,160
Let's meet up sometime.

94
00:06:04,580 --> 00:06:07,920
[BBQ]

95
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:05,830
Ma'am.

96
00:06:05,830 --> 00:06:06,830
Is everyone here?

97
00:06:07,160 --> 00:06:07,800
They're waiting for you.

98
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:08,600
In the back.

99
00:06:09,040 --> 00:06:09,800
I'll take you there.

100
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:10,800
This way, please.

101
00:06:11,560 --> 00:06:12,430
There are others?

102
00:06:12,430 --> 00:06:13,480
All the way in the back.

103
00:06:13,480 --> 00:06:14,610
Got it. You go ahead.

104
00:06:14,610 --> 00:06:17,150
[Spicy]

105
00:06:15,160 --> 00:06:15,920
Who's it?

106
00:06:27,310 --> 00:06:27,940
Mr. Guo,

107
00:06:28,350 --> 00:06:29,540
I've invited her here.

108
00:06:29,540 --> 00:06:31,100
You should do the talking.

109
00:06:33,310 --> 00:06:34,250
Chef Li,

110
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:37,040
all those problems
in the Chinese restaurant—

111
00:06:37,040 --> 00:06:38,770
I didn't cause them on purpose.

112
00:06:39,040 --> 00:06:39,560
But

113
00:06:39,560 --> 00:06:40,690
I didn't do anything to stop it.

114
00:06:40,690 --> 00:06:42,040
I failed in my duty.

115
00:06:42,040 --> 00:06:44,040
I, Guo Luda, cannot shirk the blame.

116
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:45,720
Of course,

117
00:06:45,720 --> 00:06:46,830
bringing this up now

118
00:06:46,830 --> 00:06:48,890
seems a bit like beating a dead horse.

119
00:06:49,040 --> 00:06:51,240
But these are truly my honest thoughts.

120
00:06:51,560 --> 00:06:52,720
When the Chinese restaurant opened,

121
00:06:52,720 --> 00:06:54,360
I really didn't swap the cured pork.

122
00:06:54,360 --> 00:06:55,480
I'm not well-educated,

123
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:56,720
but I know right from wrong.

124
00:06:56,720 --> 00:06:58,430
If I had done something like that,

125
00:06:58,430 --> 00:07:01,290
my late master wouldn't
forgive me, even in heaven.

126
00:07:04,600 --> 00:07:05,560
Chef,

127
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:07,240
my brothers and I here

128
00:07:07,240 --> 00:07:08,720
are neither Chef Jia's men

129
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:10,120
nor Wei's men.

130
00:07:10,480 --> 00:07:11,120
We all

131
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:13,560
studied under Zheng Shuolin,
the great Huaiyang cuisine master.

132
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:14,800
We started from

133
00:07:14,800 --> 00:07:16,360
small family restaurants,

134
00:07:16,560 --> 00:07:18,560
got bought out by Purong Hotel,

135
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:20,160
and stayed on in the kitchen.

136
00:07:20,240 --> 00:07:22,500
We earned our place here with real skill.

137
00:07:22,720 --> 00:07:24,920
I hope you can see that.

138
00:07:26,720 --> 00:07:27,780
Let's go in and sit.

139
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:29,560
There are still many things you don't know

140
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:31,020
that they want to tell you.

141
00:07:33,720 --> 00:07:35,360
Then take a seat, chefs.

142
00:07:37,360 --> 00:07:38,159
Ma'am.

143
00:07:39,159 --> 00:07:41,090
We'll take 200 lamb skewers first.

144
00:07:41,159 --> 00:07:42,920
Okay, coming right up.

145
00:07:43,480 --> 00:07:44,040
Cheers.

146
00:07:44,800 --> 00:07:45,360
Cheers.

147
00:07:49,450 --> 00:07:52,780
[Purong By Your Side]

148
00:07:50,390 --> 00:07:51,159
Come in.

149
00:07:54,390 --> 00:07:55,240
Ms. Yang,

150
00:07:56,040 --> 00:07:57,000
you're looking for me?

151
00:07:57,000 --> 00:07:57,830
Ms. Xu,

152
00:07:58,240 --> 00:07:59,040
you applied

153
00:07:59,040 --> 00:08:01,560
for the career direction
assessment test, right?

154
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:02,270
Yes.

155
00:08:02,270 --> 00:08:03,560
But I'm not qualified

156
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:05,240
to take this test yet, right?

157
00:08:05,360 --> 00:08:06,600
The general manager's office

158
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:07,830
has reformed the employee

159
00:08:07,830 --> 00:08:09,000
development system.

160
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:10,560
Employees who‘ve been here
for less than a year

161
00:08:10,560 --> 00:08:11,390
are now also entitled to know

162
00:08:11,390 --> 00:08:12,720
their career potential.

163
00:08:12,720 --> 00:08:13,360
I called you here

164
00:08:13,360 --> 00:08:14,390
just to let you know

165
00:08:14,390 --> 00:08:16,760
that you can take the test anytime.

166
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:18,960
That's great. Thank you.

167
00:08:21,690 --> 00:08:23,870
[Purong Hotel
Career Direction Assessment Test]

168
00:08:21,830 --> 00:08:23,360
The test will take about

169
00:08:23,360 --> 00:08:25,000
45 to 60 minutes.

170
00:08:23,870 --> 00:08:24,830
[Work order]

171
00:08:24,850 --> 00:08:26,650
[Expenses] [Expenses Items]
[Your Authority (yuan): ]

172
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:26,390
Just try to stay relaxed

173
00:08:26,390 --> 00:08:27,830
while you're completing it.

174
00:08:26,680 --> 00:08:27,600
[Work time]

175
00:08:27,830 --> 00:08:28,600
Thank you.

176
00:08:39,340 --> 00:08:41,980
[Name: Xu Miyu]

177
00:08:52,670 --> 00:08:55,440
Purong represents a classic style of life

178
00:08:55,070 --> 00:09:02,940
[Purong Hotel]

179
00:08:55,510 --> 00:08:57,310
and a kind of top-level dignity.

180
00:08:57,480 --> 00:08:58,360
But

181
00:08:58,360 --> 00:08:59,390
at its core, a hotel

182
00:08:59,390 --> 00:09:00,960
exists to serve its guests

183
00:09:01,030 --> 00:09:03,030
and the people who live in this city.

184
00:09:03,030 --> 00:09:03,940
So,

185
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:05,390
what's important

186
00:09:05,390 --> 00:09:07,520
is stay connected with current trends

187
00:09:07,550 --> 00:09:09,670
and promote the Purong lifestyle

188
00:09:09,670 --> 00:09:11,390
to more guests.

189
00:09:17,590 --> 00:09:18,280
True.

190
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:21,000
Adding items that interest customers

191
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:22,840
does help boost revenue.

192
00:09:23,200 --> 00:09:23,960
So,

193
00:09:24,270 --> 00:09:25,600
colleagues from sales—

194
00:09:25,620 --> 00:09:26,980
[Customer Repurchase Intention Survey]

195
00:09:25,930 --> 00:09:28,060
We're planning to launch a new package

196
00:09:28,080 --> 00:09:29,170
for the 520 promotion.

197
00:09:29,170 --> 00:09:30,290
Ms. Xu,

198
00:09:30,320 --> 00:09:31,890
there's noise in Room 1810.

199
00:09:31,740 --> 00:09:32,820
[Customer Repurchase Intention Survey]

200
00:09:31,910 --> 00:09:34,370
The guest next door
has already complained.

201
00:09:35,670 --> 00:09:36,800
I'll be right there.

202
00:10:01,730 --> 00:10:03,120
Look.

203
00:10:10,240 --> 00:10:11,000
Miyu.

204
00:10:11,680 --> 00:10:13,330
These are my old friends.

205
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:14,840
None of us have anything to do now.

206
00:10:14,840 --> 00:10:15,630
so we're just

207
00:10:15,630 --> 00:10:16,510
having fun.

208
00:10:17,840 --> 00:10:18,860
Daniel,

209
00:10:18,940 --> 00:10:20,480
I understand what you want to do,

210
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:21,630
but

211
00:10:21,630 --> 00:10:24,060
the hotel is a semi-public
place after all.

212
00:10:24,120 --> 00:10:26,480
Other guests are already complaining.

213
00:10:26,480 --> 00:10:27,840
So if you want to rehearse together,

214
00:10:27,840 --> 00:10:30,440
you probably can't do it
on the executive floor

215
00:10:31,150 --> 00:10:32,750
It is a bit disturbing.

216
00:10:33,750 --> 00:10:35,630
But where can we go?

217
00:10:38,150 --> 00:10:39,480
Let me figure this out.

218
00:10:51,910 --> 00:10:53,310
Watch out for the uphill.

219
00:11:00,120 --> 00:11:01,120
Here we are.

220
00:11:08,550 --> 00:11:09,070
Come.

221
00:11:09,390 --> 00:11:10,290
Come on.

222
00:11:14,280 --> 00:11:15,160
Be careful.

223
00:11:18,320 --> 00:11:18,910
Look.

224
00:11:19,720 --> 00:11:20,850
This place

225
00:11:20,880 --> 00:11:22,000
doesn't have many people around.

226
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:23,360
There are warehouses on both sides,

227
00:11:23,360 --> 00:11:24,600
so it won't disturb anyone's work.

228
00:11:24,600 --> 00:11:26,240
It's perfect for your rehearsals.

229
00:11:26,240 --> 00:11:27,000
Also,

230
00:11:27,000 --> 00:11:29,200
I've prepared power strips and chairs.

231
00:11:30,130 --> 00:11:31,940
There is a clothes rack here

232
00:11:32,110 --> 00:11:34,060
for you to hang your clothes.

233
00:11:35,180 --> 00:11:36,300
Miyu.

234
00:11:36,370 --> 00:11:37,380
Fantastic.

235
00:11:38,000 --> 00:11:39,000
How's it, old friends?

236
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:39,600
Great.

237
00:11:41,130 --> 00:11:42,130
Good.

238
00:11:43,750 --> 00:11:44,880
This is outrageous.

239
00:11:45,210 --> 00:11:47,450
You secretly moved
a band with an average age of over 70

240
00:11:47,260 --> 00:11:49,590
[Purong Hotel]

241
00:11:47,480 --> 00:11:48,840
to the basement warehouse.

242
00:11:48,840 --> 00:11:50,000
What were you thinking?

243
00:11:50,000 --> 00:11:51,480
I know that place has no windows

244
00:11:51,480 --> 00:11:52,550
and poor ventilation.

245
00:11:52,550 --> 00:11:54,000
So I agreed with them

246
00:11:54,000 --> 00:11:56,000
that daily rehearsals
can't exceed one hour.

247
00:11:56,000 --> 00:11:58,000
If any accidents happen within that hour,

248
00:11:58,000 --> 00:11:59,530
how do you plan to handle it?

249
00:12:00,720 --> 00:12:01,580
I'm sorry.

250
00:12:02,000 --> 00:12:03,600
I’ll go find another place.

251
00:12:05,640 --> 00:12:07,300
Why didn't you ask me for help?

252
00:12:16,530 --> 00:12:17,630
Forget it.

253
00:12:18,120 --> 00:12:19,720
Bring the seniors out first.

254
00:12:19,840 --> 00:12:20,630
From now on,

255
00:12:20,630 --> 00:12:21,720
don't let guests

256
00:12:22,120 --> 00:12:24,520
use that storage room without my approval.

257
00:12:35,810 --> 00:12:36,810
Help me check

258
00:12:36,840 --> 00:12:37,480
all the currently available

259
00:12:37,480 --> 00:12:38,910
empty spaces in the hotel.

260
00:12:38,910 --> 00:12:39,860
Soundproof

261
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:41,240
and well-ventilated.

262
00:12:41,240 --> 00:12:43,320
Ms. Xu just left with a long face.

263
00:12:43,320 --> 00:12:44,000
Thank you.

264
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:45,480
Did you pick on her again?

265
00:12:44,790 --> 00:12:48,670
[Purong Hotel]

266
00:12:45,720 --> 00:12:47,000
Who picked on her?

267
00:12:49,240 --> 00:12:49,840
Wait.

268
00:12:50,840 --> 00:12:53,300
Is there something
going on between you two?

269
00:12:53,400 --> 00:12:54,790
Just get to the point.

270
00:12:56,510 --> 00:12:57,840
Mr. Zheng from the Lusia University

271
00:12:57,840 --> 00:12:58,960
Alumni Association

272
00:12:58,960 --> 00:13:00,450
will be here soon.

273
00:13:01,120 --> 00:13:02,240
He wants to go over

274
00:13:02,240 --> 00:13:05,170
the activity flow
for the 60th anniversary reunion.

275
00:13:05,360 --> 00:13:06,960
Isn't it basically settled?

276
00:13:07,120 --> 00:13:09,430
They want to add a small request.

277
00:13:09,510 --> 00:13:10,240
They said they'd like

278
00:13:10,240 --> 00:13:12,240
to look for the old Shanghai vibe.

279
00:13:12,360 --> 00:13:14,240
Should we put on a cheongsam show

280
00:13:14,240 --> 00:13:16,720
or a medley of classic old songs?

281
00:13:17,000 --> 00:13:18,360
If we really turn the banquet hall

282
00:13:18,360 --> 00:13:20,000
into old Shanghai style,

283
00:13:20,000 --> 00:13:20,840
then we will

284
00:13:21,240 --> 00:13:22,840
have to spend more money.

285
00:13:24,240 --> 00:13:25,480
And we might

286
00:13:25,480 --> 00:13:26,480
mess it up.

287
00:13:28,120 --> 00:13:28,960
It's too hard.

288
00:13:33,710 --> 00:13:34,360
Old man.

289
00:13:34,360 --> 00:13:36,020
Take one more step. I dare you.

290
00:13:36,270 --> 00:13:37,980
I've told you many times.

291
00:13:38,080 --> 00:13:38,720
Daniel,

292
00:13:39,120 --> 00:13:40,240
my colleagues
from the Engineering Department

293
00:13:40,240 --> 00:13:41,600
are just doing their job.

294
00:13:41,600 --> 00:13:42,440
The main issue

295
00:13:42,440 --> 00:13:43,720
is this place is too risky.

296
00:13:43,720 --> 00:13:45,480
The hotel cannot bear this responsibility.

297
00:13:45,480 --> 00:13:46,740
What responsibility?

298
00:13:46,750 --> 00:13:48,480
To put it bluntly,
you're afraid we'll die here,

299
00:13:48,480 --> 00:13:49,120
right?

300
00:13:49,600 --> 00:13:52,320
Drawing a conclusion
without considering probability—

301
00:13:52,320 --> 00:13:53,480
that's a bit rogue.

302
00:13:53,840 --> 00:13:55,290
Daniel, calm down.

303
00:13:55,340 --> 00:13:57,000
The hotel has its concerns,

304
00:13:57,000 --> 00:13:58,510
but it's mainly to ensure

305
00:13:58,510 --> 00:14:00,720
the health and safety of the guests.

306
00:14:00,720 --> 00:14:02,650
Ji Feng told you to say this, right?

307
00:14:04,120 --> 00:14:06,600
Go ask him. I helped him

308
00:14:06,600 --> 00:14:08,110
fix the Chinese restaurant's design,

309
00:14:08,110 --> 00:14:09,770
and now he turns his back on me?

310
00:14:10,360 --> 00:14:11,440
If he's got the guts,

311
00:14:11,440 --> 00:14:13,240
let him come kick us out himself.

312
00:14:13,320 --> 00:14:14,780
It's a misunderstanding.

313
00:14:15,480 --> 00:14:17,000
Definitely a misunderstanding.

314
00:14:17,000 --> 00:14:17,720
Look,

315
00:14:18,510 --> 00:14:20,110
it's too stuffy here,

316
00:14:20,140 --> 00:14:21,670
and the air quality is poor.

317
00:14:21,720 --> 00:14:23,710
Ms. Xu and I discussed it.

318
00:14:24,080 --> 00:14:25,120
Right next

319
00:14:25,120 --> 00:14:25,980
to

320
00:14:26,010 --> 00:14:26,870
the restaurant on the second floor,

321
00:14:26,870 --> 00:14:28,440
we've set aside a space

322
00:14:28,480 --> 00:14:29,880
just for you to rehearse.

323
00:14:30,320 --> 00:14:31,360
If you're willing

324
00:14:31,360 --> 00:14:32,840
to move upstairs,

325
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:33,480
no one

326
00:14:33,480 --> 00:14:35,010
will ever bother you again.

327
00:14:35,200 --> 00:14:36,630
You can focus on

328
00:14:36,630 --> 00:14:37,470
practicing.

329
00:14:38,480 --> 00:14:39,240
Really?

330
00:14:42,640 --> 00:14:44,010
How about we go and have a look first?

331
00:14:44,010 --> 00:14:45,240
-See if you like it.
-Yes.

332
00:14:45,240 --> 00:14:46,120
That's fine.

333
00:14:46,840 --> 00:14:47,840
We can take a look.

334
00:14:47,870 --> 00:14:48,800
I'll take you up.

335
00:14:48,830 --> 00:14:49,350
Come on.

336
00:14:51,120 --> 00:14:51,840
Come.

337
00:14:54,720 --> 00:14:55,360
Please.

338
00:14:59,840 --> 00:15:00,600
Not bad.

339
00:15:01,240 --> 00:15:02,240
What do you think?

340
00:15:04,320 --> 00:15:05,480
Not bad.

341
00:15:09,480 --> 00:15:10,360
Not bad.

342
00:15:11,120 --> 00:15:13,200
The environment here isn't the best yet,

343
00:15:13,200 --> 00:15:14,320
But don't worry,

344
00:15:14,480 --> 00:15:15,880
we'll keep improving it.

345
00:15:16,230 --> 00:15:17,510
But...

346
00:15:17,510 --> 00:15:19,120
nothing comes for free.

347
00:15:20,120 --> 00:15:21,440
Are you

348
00:15:21,840 --> 00:15:23,440
asking me for another favor?

349
00:15:25,000 --> 00:15:25,630
As expected,

350
00:15:25,630 --> 00:15:27,830
I can't hide anything from you, Mr. Tan.

351
00:15:28,000 --> 00:15:29,440
I do have something

352
00:15:29,440 --> 00:15:30,480
that I hope you can help with.

353
00:15:30,480 --> 00:15:31,120
Tell me.

354
00:15:33,870 --> 00:15:35,960
The alumni reunion of Lusia University

355
00:15:35,960 --> 00:15:37,690
is going to be held at our hotel.

356
00:15:37,720 --> 00:15:38,720
The attendees are all

357
00:15:38,720 --> 00:15:40,360
elderly people.

358
00:15:40,360 --> 00:15:41,480
And what they want to hear the most

359
00:15:41,480 --> 00:15:42,200
are the claasic

360
00:15:42,200 --> 00:15:43,790
old Shanghai jazz tunes

361
00:15:43,960 --> 00:15:46,120
from their younger days.

362
00:15:46,870 --> 00:15:48,000
That's exactly

363
00:15:48,000 --> 00:15:49,860
the kind of music you love to play.

364
00:15:50,120 --> 00:15:51,120
And you guys are here

365
00:15:51,120 --> 00:15:52,720
at our hotel at the same time.

366
00:15:52,960 --> 00:15:53,750
So,

367
00:15:54,060 --> 00:15:55,300
maybe it's fate.

368
00:15:58,840 --> 00:15:59,580
That's good.

369
00:16:04,750 --> 00:16:05,840
Great.

370
00:16:06,120 --> 00:16:07,400
It's fate.

371
00:16:15,000 --> 00:16:15,600
Ms. Xu.

372
00:16:17,840 --> 00:16:19,340
I didn't discuss this

373
00:16:19,450 --> 00:16:20,800
with you beforehand.

374
00:16:21,840 --> 00:16:23,120
Mr. Ji, you don't need

375
00:16:23,120 --> 00:16:25,180
my opinion for any decision you make.

376
00:16:25,240 --> 00:16:26,480
Besides, this is my job.

377
00:16:26,480 --> 00:16:27,600
I didn't do it well.

378
00:16:27,600 --> 00:16:29,080
I'll go back and reflect on it.

379
00:16:29,080 --> 00:16:30,080
Don't say that.

380
00:16:30,080 --> 00:16:32,430
Meeting the guests' needs
is your responsibility.

381
00:16:32,430 --> 00:16:34,200
Supporting you is mine.

382
00:16:37,360 --> 00:16:38,950
I mean—

383
00:16:38,980 --> 00:16:41,110
a superior supporting a subordinate.

384
00:16:44,840 --> 00:16:46,840
I have something else to do. I'll...

385
00:16:47,360 --> 00:16:48,690
No matter what happens,

386
00:16:48,750 --> 00:16:50,150
I hope you won't avoid me.

387
00:16:50,720 --> 00:16:52,420
I'm your superior.

388
00:16:52,790 --> 00:16:54,360
I will take responsibility for you.

389
00:16:54,360 --> 00:16:56,020
You can trust me a little more,

390
00:16:56,200 --> 00:16:56,750
okay?

391
00:17:00,480 --> 00:17:02,140
I've said what I needed to say.

392
00:17:05,440 --> 00:17:06,240
Coming?

393
00:17:16,720 --> 00:17:17,589
According

394
00:17:17,589 --> 00:17:18,720
to the data from our

395
00:17:18,720 --> 00:17:20,240
Business Management Department,

396
00:17:20,240 --> 00:17:22,109
the Chinese restaurant's revenue
has hit a new high

397
00:17:22,109 --> 00:17:23,970
in the first week since it  opened.

398
00:17:24,589 --> 00:17:27,790
The occupancy rate of
HSKP Department is also steadily climbing—

399
00:17:27,790 --> 00:17:29,390
far beyond our projections.

400
00:17:33,030 --> 00:17:34,720
That's enough of the good news.

401
00:17:34,720 --> 00:17:36,000
Next, let's have

402
00:17:36,000 --> 00:17:37,110
Mr. Xue

403
00:17:37,110 --> 00:17:37,830
brief us

404
00:17:37,830 --> 00:17:39,560
on tomorrow's reception work.

405
00:17:48,550 --> 00:17:50,400
The number of the alumni group tomorrow

406
00:17:50,400 --> 00:17:51,310
is over 100.

407
00:17:51,720 --> 00:17:52,380
Among them,

408
00:17:52,830 --> 00:17:54,720
there are 68 seniors

409
00:17:54,720 --> 00:17:56,120
who are over 80 years old.

410
00:17:56,640 --> 00:17:58,110
We need to accommodate their needs

411
00:17:58,110 --> 00:17:59,430
as much as possible.

412
00:17:59,510 --> 00:18:00,240
For example,

413
00:18:00,240 --> 00:18:01,880
the lighting and ventilation

414
00:18:01,880 --> 00:18:02,940
in the guest rooms,

415
00:18:03,110 --> 00:18:05,240
and the guests' dietary preferences.

416
00:18:05,440 --> 00:18:06,440
If necessary,

417
00:18:06,440 --> 00:18:08,570
we can provide some medical services.

418
00:18:12,310 --> 00:18:12,960
Hello.

419
00:18:13,000 --> 00:18:14,130
I'd like to check in.

420
00:18:16,400 --> 00:18:18,600
You'd like a south-facing room, right?

421
00:18:18,640 --> 00:18:19,110
Yes.

422
00:18:19,240 --> 00:18:20,370
Let me check for you.

423
00:18:20,840 --> 00:18:23,690
[Room Status Center]

424
00:18:25,340 --> 00:18:29,110
[Executive Room 1812]

425
00:18:28,790 --> 00:18:29,640
He...

426
00:18:30,190 --> 00:18:31,400
checked out?

427
00:18:43,220 --> 00:18:44,960
♪ A flicker of dim light ♪

428
00:18:46,730 --> 00:18:48,370
♪ A bowl of warm soup ♪

429
00:18:50,590 --> 00:18:52,500
♪ People in the city ♪

430
00:18:53,320 --> 00:18:56,260
♪ Squeezing into the hustle and bustle ♪

431
00:18:58,190 --> 00:19:00,000
♪ The palms of time ♪

432
00:19:01,900 --> 00:19:05,040
♪ Grinding away the simple days ♪

433
00:19:05,650 --> 00:19:08,570
♪ Sprinkling them into this busy world ♪

434
00:19:09,570 --> 00:19:11,610
♪ To be tasted, bit by bit ♪

435
00:19:13,090 --> 00:19:16,290
♪ Embracing this radiant world ♪

436
00:19:16,880 --> 00:19:19,910
♪ Keeps the heart from fading to grey ♪

437
00:19:20,500 --> 00:19:23,620
♪ Life's joy, sorrow, cold, and warmth ♪

438
00:19:24,360 --> 00:19:26,840
♪ Intertwined within the mundane ♪

439
00:19:27,010 --> 00:19:28,210
Room service.

440
00:19:28,400 --> 00:19:31,710
♪ Let us bravely gather up ♪

441
00:19:32,260 --> 00:19:35,630
♪ The forgotten past ♪

442
00:19:36,440 --> 00:19:37,820
Good morning, Mr. Ji.

443
00:19:36,610 --> 00:19:38,880
♪ There may be regrets ♪

444
00:19:39,590 --> 00:19:40,030
Hello, Mr. Ji.

445
00:19:40,030 --> 00:19:41,380
I am the 10th-floor forewoman.

446
00:19:40,540 --> 00:19:42,780
♪ There may be loneliness ♪

447
00:19:41,400 --> 00:19:43,660
Feel free to call me if you need anything.

448
00:19:43,770 --> 00:19:44,640
Thank you.

449
00:20:12,400 --> 00:20:16,530
[Lusia University Alumni Association
Anniversary Reunion]

450
00:20:16,670 --> 00:20:17,640
[Alumni Association of Lusia University]

451
00:20:17,660 --> 00:20:19,470
[60th Anniversary of Establishment]

452
00:20:21,400 --> 00:20:22,310
The car to the airport

453
00:20:22,310 --> 00:20:23,550
has already left.

454
00:20:24,880 --> 00:20:26,080
Why go to the airport?

455
00:20:30,590 --> 00:20:31,660
Sorry.

456
00:20:31,680 --> 00:20:32,400
My mistake.

457
00:20:32,430 --> 00:20:33,160
Go on.

458
00:20:34,710 --> 00:20:36,110
Two shuttles each
in the morning and afternoon.

459
00:20:36,110 --> 00:20:37,390
That should guarantee

460
00:20:37,440 --> 00:20:38,480
none of the guests

461
00:20:38,480 --> 00:20:39,720
from the Lusia Alumni Association

462
00:20:39,720 --> 00:20:42,310
wait more than
half an hour at the airport.

463
00:20:47,680 --> 00:20:48,480
What's wrong?

464
00:20:48,640 --> 00:20:51,040
Moving rooms got you feeling sentimental?

465
00:20:52,780 --> 00:20:53,580
Not at all.

466
00:20:57,000 --> 00:20:58,460
Just make do for a few days.

467
00:20:58,720 --> 00:21:00,720
Once the alumni association leaves,

468
00:21:00,720 --> 00:21:02,890
I'll give 1812 back to you right away.

469
00:21:03,660 --> 00:21:05,190
I'm fine staying anywhere.

470
00:21:06,840 --> 00:21:07,400
By the way,

471
00:21:07,400 --> 00:21:09,330
has the car to the airport left yet?

472
00:21:11,790 --> 00:21:12,680
Mr. Ji,

473
00:21:13,240 --> 00:21:15,040
what was I just reporting to you?

474
00:21:17,510 --> 00:21:20,000
I... I asked the wrong question.
I meant to ask about

475
00:21:20,000 --> 00:21:20,480
the banquet hall.

476
00:21:20,480 --> 00:21:22,400
16 tables, 182 people.

477
00:21:25,480 --> 00:21:26,480
By the way, Mr. Ji.

478
00:21:27,240 --> 00:21:29,700
How many alumni are coming
to reunion again?

479
00:21:41,000 --> 00:21:41,750
Mr. Ji,

480
00:21:42,790 --> 00:21:44,720
who exactly is on your mind?

481
00:21:45,680 --> 00:21:46,720
No one.

482
00:21:46,720 --> 00:21:48,240
I stayed up late last night

483
00:21:48,240 --> 00:21:49,550
and didn't sleep well.

484
00:21:49,550 --> 00:21:50,750
My brain is a bit slow.

485
00:21:51,270 --> 00:21:52,870
You're just being stubborn.

486
00:21:53,160 --> 00:21:54,270
As your senior,

487
00:21:54,720 --> 00:21:56,920
let me give you a little piece of advice.

488
00:21:57,480 --> 00:21:59,240
When your heart starts churning,

489
00:21:59,240 --> 00:22:01,680
just think of Duan Aoxiang
staring you down.

490
00:22:01,680 --> 00:22:02,720
And think about

491
00:22:02,720 --> 00:22:05,180
the cutthroat competition in the industry.

492
00:22:06,240 --> 00:22:07,300
Works pretty well.

493
00:22:08,240 --> 00:22:09,440
What are you talking about?

494
00:22:09,440 --> 00:22:10,570
I don't understand.

495
00:22:10,920 --> 00:22:12,180
I'm going out for a bit.

496
00:22:16,750 --> 00:22:17,480
Mr. Ji.

497
00:22:18,000 --> 00:22:18,720
What is it?

498
00:22:19,720 --> 00:22:20,430
Mr. Ji,

499
00:22:20,640 --> 00:22:22,240
I'm here to deliver
the candidate materials

500
00:22:22,240 --> 00:22:24,240
for the front office lobby manager.

501
00:22:24,960 --> 00:22:26,510
Isn't Anna about to take maternity leave?

502
00:22:26,510 --> 00:22:27,440
Director Bai said

503
00:22:27,440 --> 00:22:30,040
we need to fill
the lobby manager role quickly.

504
00:22:30,210 --> 00:22:33,720
[Employee Internal Promotion
Application Form]

505
00:22:34,020 --> 00:22:40,410
[Lusia University Alumni Association
Anniversary Reunion]

506
00:22:36,270 --> 00:22:37,200
Put it here.

507
00:22:39,240 --> 00:22:40,700
A little further forward.

508
00:22:52,930 --> 00:22:53,480
Let me help you.

509
00:22:53,480 --> 00:22:54,680
Thanks, but I'm fine.

510
00:22:55,160 --> 00:22:56,720
Help me with the luggage.

511
00:22:56,720 --> 00:22:58,050
Okay. This way, please.

512
00:23:03,820 --> 00:23:04,500
[Alumni Association of Lusia University]

513
00:23:03,960 --> 00:23:04,880
Jialing!

514
00:23:04,520 --> 00:23:05,620
[60th Anniversary of Establishment]

515
00:23:05,790 --> 00:23:07,080
You're back too!

516
00:23:09,440 --> 00:23:10,720
My old deskmate!

517
00:23:10,720 --> 00:23:12,440
I've missed you so much!

518
00:23:12,550 --> 00:23:13,720
Meilan,

519
00:23:13,720 --> 00:23:15,440
it's been so many years.

520
00:23:15,440 --> 00:23:17,340
I'm so happy today.

521
00:23:18,070 --> 00:23:19,440
I'll take you to see Wang.

522
00:23:19,440 --> 00:23:21,240
He's been waiting for us all morning.

523
00:23:21,240 --> 00:23:22,310
Okay.

524
00:23:23,160 --> 00:23:25,480
It's been so many years.

525
00:23:29,440 --> 00:23:29,790
Hello.

526
00:23:29,790 --> 00:23:31,160
Your room is on the third floor.

527
00:23:31,160 --> 00:23:32,030
The elevator is over there.

528
00:23:32,030 --> 00:23:33,680
Just walk in that direction.

529
00:23:33,920 --> 00:23:34,640
Welcome.

530
00:23:40,640 --> 00:23:42,480
Why is there
such a long line at the reception?

531
00:23:42,480 --> 00:23:43,680
Clear it out quickly.

532
00:23:43,880 --> 00:23:45,000
Open another line here.

533
00:23:45,000 --> 00:23:45,720
Copy that.

534
00:23:46,640 --> 00:23:48,000
The reception is short of staff.

535
00:23:48,000 --> 00:23:48,730
We need help.

536
00:23:49,240 --> 00:23:50,000
Xu,

537
00:23:50,000 --> 00:23:51,070
the reception is short of staff.

538
00:23:51,070 --> 00:23:52,840
Come help with the check-in.

539
00:23:53,000 --> 00:23:53,480
Okay.

540
00:23:56,720 --> 00:23:57,510
Ms. An,

541
00:23:57,510 --> 00:23:58,400
are you okay?

542
00:24:03,270 --> 00:24:04,270
You go

543
00:24:04,750 --> 00:24:06,790
and turn on the check-in system first.

544
00:24:06,790 --> 00:24:07,650
I need a moment.

545
00:24:07,720 --> 00:24:08,510
Okay.

546
00:24:28,030 --> 00:24:29,100
Ms. Xu.

547
00:24:30,030 --> 00:24:30,860
Do you have

548
00:24:30,960 --> 00:24:33,290
a printed list of executive floor guests?

549
00:24:33,480 --> 00:24:34,720
All the guest lists are here.

550
00:24:34,720 --> 00:24:35,920
Look for yourselves.

551
00:24:36,720 --> 00:24:38,270
We'll go blind reading this.

552
00:24:38,270 --> 00:24:39,240
Ms. Xu,

553
00:24:39,240 --> 00:24:41,270
-I'll go back to the executive floor.
-Wait.

554
00:24:41,270 --> 00:24:42,730
I have a digital copy here.

555
00:24:42,890 --> 00:24:44,350
We'll print it ourselves.

556
00:24:44,790 --> 00:24:45,640
Give it to me.

557
00:24:48,720 --> 00:24:49,510
Ms. An.

558
00:24:50,480 --> 00:24:51,680
Ms. Xu,

559
00:24:51,680 --> 00:24:53,140
that's thoughtful of you.

560
00:24:53,270 --> 00:24:54,640
You don't look well.

561
00:24:54,640 --> 00:24:55,720
Go rest for a while.

562
00:24:56,720 --> 00:24:57,480
I'm fine.

563
00:24:58,030 --> 00:24:59,400
Thanks for your help.

564
00:24:59,480 --> 00:25:00,270
Be careful.

565
00:25:07,720 --> 00:25:08,310
Let me do it.

566
00:25:08,310 --> 00:25:08,720
Okay.

567
00:25:12,030 --> 00:25:12,750
Everyone,

568
00:25:13,070 --> 00:25:14,720
you can check in here too.

569
00:25:19,510 --> 00:25:20,400
Welcome.

570
00:25:21,400 --> 00:25:22,930
Help me find the materials.

571
00:25:25,270 --> 00:25:26,400
Please show your ID.

572
00:25:32,070 --> 00:25:33,310
No, this is too slow.

573
00:25:35,720 --> 00:25:37,720
Huanhuan, lend me your microphone.

574
00:25:37,720 --> 00:25:38,980
Xiaoyan, microphone.

575
00:25:43,070 --> 00:25:45,030
Dear guests
of the Lusia Alumni Association,

576
00:25:45,030 --> 00:25:46,070
hello, everyone,

577
00:25:46,160 --> 00:25:48,320
welcome to Purong Hotel.

578
00:25:48,400 --> 00:25:50,400
Next, the guests whose names I call,

579
00:25:50,400 --> 00:25:52,000
please bring your passports

580
00:25:52,000 --> 00:25:52,920
and come to me.

581
00:25:52,920 --> 00:25:54,550
I will take everyone upstairs

582
00:25:54,550 --> 00:25:56,240
to check in, okay?

583
00:25:57,480 --> 00:25:59,460
First, Ms. Fu Meilan.

584
00:25:59,640 --> 00:26:00,640
I'm here.

585
00:26:01,240 --> 00:26:01,590
This way.

586
00:26:01,590 --> 00:26:02,590
This way, please.

587
00:26:03,240 --> 00:26:04,640
Mr. Jing Zekai.

588
00:26:05,270 --> 00:26:06,000
Here.

589
00:26:06,240 --> 00:26:07,400
Ms. Qin Jialing.

590
00:26:07,720 --> 00:26:08,510
Here.

591
00:26:11,510 --> 00:26:13,270
M-My passport is in this suitcase.

592
00:26:13,270 --> 00:26:14,240
In the suitcase.

593
00:26:16,000 --> 00:26:16,550
It's fine.

594
00:26:16,550 --> 00:26:18,030
Who put this on top of it?

595
00:26:18,030 --> 00:26:19,200
Wait a moment.

596
00:26:19,480 --> 00:26:20,030
It's okay.

597
00:26:20,030 --> 00:26:20,720
Okay.

598
00:26:21,480 --> 00:26:22,270
Oh, really.

599
00:26:23,880 --> 00:26:24,750
I've got it.

600
00:26:29,290 --> 00:26:30,420
[Qin 1802]

601
00:26:30,640 --> 00:26:32,000
Please go upstairs and check in first.

602
00:26:32,000 --> 00:26:33,160
The bellman will bring your luggage

603
00:26:33,160 --> 00:26:34,240
to your room later.

604
00:26:34,240 --> 00:26:35,240
Thank you.

605
00:26:35,240 --> 00:26:36,170
You're welcome.

606
00:26:36,790 --> 00:26:37,660
Please follow me this way.

607
00:26:37,660 --> 00:26:38,510
Okay.

608
00:26:38,510 --> 00:26:39,480
Next,

609
00:26:40,000 --> 00:26:41,820
Mr. Xiao Qiankun.

610
00:26:42,070 --> 00:26:43,670
Hello, welcome to our hotel.

611
00:26:49,880 --> 00:26:50,480
Ms. An,

612
00:26:50,480 --> 00:26:51,280
what's wrong?

613
00:26:53,240 --> 00:26:54,480
Ms. An! Ms. An!

614
00:26:55,640 --> 00:26:56,720
Ms. An!

615
00:26:57,000 --> 00:26:58,000
-Ms. An!
-What’s wrong?

616
00:26:58,000 --> 00:26:59,100
Ms. An!

617
00:26:59,130 --> 00:27:00,270
Ms. An!

618
00:27:00,510 --> 00:27:01,480
Ms. An!

619
00:27:01,570 --> 00:27:02,480
Lay her flat.

620
00:27:03,000 --> 00:27:04,070
What should we do?

621
00:27:04,070 --> 00:27:06,600
Well, Director Bai isn't here either.

622
00:27:06,720 --> 00:27:07,780
Call an ambulance!

623
00:27:07,790 --> 00:27:09,310
Right, call an ambulance.

624
00:27:11,070 --> 00:27:11,880
Ms. An.

625
00:27:13,070 --> 00:27:13,880
It'll be fine.

626
00:27:14,000 --> 00:27:15,270
The ambulance will be here soon.

627
00:27:15,270 --> 00:27:16,480
Hello, 911?

628
00:27:16,790 --> 00:27:18,240
This is Purong Hotel.

629
00:27:18,240 --> 00:27:19,970
A pregnant woman just fainted.

630
00:27:20,270 --> 00:27:21,550
Okay. Okay.

631
00:27:22,810 --> 00:27:24,030
[Ambulance]

632
00:27:23,640 --> 00:27:25,200
Excuse me!

633
00:27:30,400 --> 00:27:32,160
Careful.

634
00:27:32,270 --> 00:27:33,480
Which one of you is going with her?

635
00:27:33,480 --> 00:27:34,270
I'll go.

636
00:27:35,400 --> 00:27:36,240
Don't.

637
00:27:37,270 --> 00:27:38,160
You stay...

638
00:27:39,270 --> 00:27:41,400
to take care of the guests for me, okay?

639
00:27:45,270 --> 00:27:46,720
None of you need to come.

640
00:27:47,750 --> 00:27:48,640
Xiaoyan,

641
00:27:49,720 --> 00:27:51,460
call my husband

642
00:27:51,880 --> 00:27:54,090
and ask him
to take my mom to the hospital.

643
00:27:54,090 --> 00:27:55,310
Okay.

644
00:27:55,440 --> 00:27:56,880
Okay. Come on. Please make way.

645
00:27:56,880 --> 00:27:57,880
-Come on.
-Excuse me.

646
00:27:57,880 --> 00:27:59,140
Come on. Give me a hand.

647
00:28:12,400 --> 00:28:13,240
Let's go.

648
00:28:20,880 --> 00:28:21,830
Xiaoyan,

649
00:28:21,850 --> 00:28:23,000
go to the Front Office

650
00:28:23,000 --> 00:28:24,720
and get all the receptionists
who are available

651
00:28:24,720 --> 00:28:25,780
from other shifts.

652
00:28:26,510 --> 00:28:28,330
Fill in these empty spots.

653
00:28:28,400 --> 00:28:29,720
Once the pressure
at the reception eases up,

654
00:28:29,720 --> 00:28:31,320
the main hall won't be a mess.

655
00:28:31,720 --> 00:28:32,510
Go quickly.

656
00:28:34,310 --> 00:28:35,000
Hello?

657
00:28:43,790 --> 00:28:45,480
Next group of executive floor guests,

658
00:28:45,480 --> 00:28:46,400
please follow me.

659
00:28:46,400 --> 00:28:47,260
Okay. This way.

660
00:28:47,920 --> 00:28:48,920
This way, please.

661
00:28:50,270 --> 00:28:51,200
Okay, thank you.

662
00:28:57,030 --> 00:28:57,920
Young man,

663
00:28:59,270 --> 00:28:59,920
excuse me,

664
00:28:59,920 --> 00:29:01,570
is there a pharmacy nearby?

665
00:29:01,920 --> 00:29:02,720
Pharmacy?

666
00:29:02,910 --> 00:29:03,880
I really don't know.

667
00:29:03,880 --> 00:29:05,510
You can ask at the information desk.

668
00:29:05,510 --> 00:29:06,400
Information desk?

669
00:29:06,400 --> 00:29:07,030
Right.

670
00:29:07,720 --> 00:29:08,310
Xia.

671
00:29:08,720 --> 00:29:09,320
Come here.

672
00:29:09,480 --> 00:29:10,080
Come here.

673
00:29:12,750 --> 00:29:14,470
What's wrong with that gentleman?

674
00:29:14,470 --> 00:29:15,720
He asked where the pharmacy is.

675
00:29:15,720 --> 00:29:16,850
I don't know either.

676
00:29:17,000 --> 00:29:17,640
I'm going up first.

677
00:29:17,640 --> 00:29:18,510
Go ahead.

678
00:29:20,720 --> 00:29:21,480
Hello.

679
00:29:21,480 --> 00:29:22,920
How can I help you?

680
00:29:23,550 --> 00:29:24,920
Where is the information desk?

681
00:29:24,920 --> 00:29:26,160
Are you looking to buy medicine?

682
00:29:26,160 --> 00:29:26,920
Yes.

683
00:29:26,920 --> 00:29:28,240
How did you know?

684
00:29:28,720 --> 00:29:29,720
I need

685
00:29:29,720 --> 00:29:31,640
to get some diabetes medication.

686
00:29:32,030 --> 00:29:33,230
Please wait a moment.

687
00:29:35,480 --> 00:29:36,400
See if any of these

688
00:29:36,400 --> 00:29:37,400
are what you need.

689
00:29:38,980 --> 00:29:39,680
This one.

690
00:29:40,510 --> 00:29:42,240
Okay, I'll place the order now.

691
00:29:42,240 --> 00:29:43,480
It should be delivered
in about half an hour.

692
00:29:43,480 --> 00:29:44,200
Is that okay?

693
00:29:44,200 --> 00:29:45,510
Okay. Great.

694
00:29:45,640 --> 00:29:47,640
I'll have it delivered to your room.

695
00:29:48,070 --> 00:29:48,880
Room 817.

696
00:29:48,880 --> 00:29:49,720
Okay, got it. Thank you.

697
00:29:49,720 --> 00:29:50,480
Thank you.

698
00:29:59,030 --> 00:30:00,380
Xiaoxi, come help me

699
00:30:01,160 --> 00:30:02,360
move this over there.

700
00:30:02,400 --> 00:30:02,930
Let's go.

701
00:30:03,870 --> 00:30:04,920
It's a bit heavy.

702
00:30:04,920 --> 00:30:05,530
Okay.

703
00:30:07,750 --> 00:30:09,150
There's someone behind.

704
00:30:12,480 --> 00:30:13,240
Madam,

705
00:30:13,240 --> 00:30:14,480
I really don't know the answer to this.

706
00:30:14,480 --> 00:30:15,960
I'm just here to enter your information.

707
00:30:15,960 --> 00:30:16,880
If you have any questions,

708
00:30:16,880 --> 00:30:18,810
please go to the information desk.

709
00:30:18,880 --> 00:30:20,440
There's a long line behind you.

710
00:30:20,440 --> 00:30:21,310
Hello?

711
00:30:21,510 --> 00:30:22,510
Guests with questions,

712
00:30:22,510 --> 00:30:24,570
please come to the information desk.

713
00:30:25,680 --> 00:30:26,510
Come, this way.

714
00:30:26,510 --> 00:30:27,270
Please move over there.

715
00:30:27,270 --> 00:30:27,920
Thank you.

716
00:30:28,070 --> 00:30:28,920
Excuse me,

717
00:30:28,920 --> 00:30:30,780
could you get me a cup of hot water?

718
00:30:30,880 --> 00:30:31,440
Sure.

719
00:30:37,790 --> 00:30:39,090
[Passport]

720
00:30:44,550 --> 00:30:45,960
Thank you.

721
00:30:46,880 --> 00:30:47,550
Xiaoyan.

722
00:30:48,480 --> 00:30:49,510
You scared me.

723
00:30:49,510 --> 00:30:50,270
Sorry about that.

724
00:30:50,270 --> 00:30:51,070
What's wrong?

725
00:30:51,160 --> 00:30:52,960
Can you help this gentleman

726
00:30:52,960 --> 00:30:53,720
check in first?

727
00:30:53,720 --> 00:30:56,270
Mr. Jiang Zhongchen
has a herniated lumbar disc.

728
00:30:56,270 --> 00:30:58,130
He needs to lie down immediately.

729
00:30:59,960 --> 00:31:00,830
I can't do that.

730
00:31:01,000 --> 00:31:02,920
Ms. Xu, we have to go in order.

731
00:31:03,030 --> 00:31:04,860
But it's what the guest needs.

732
00:31:05,590 --> 00:31:06,350
Listen to me.

733
00:31:06,350 --> 00:31:07,280
Just ignore him.

734
00:31:08,310 --> 00:31:09,110
Tell you what.

735
00:31:09,270 --> 00:31:10,680
I'll take him to the executive floor

736
00:31:10,680 --> 00:31:11,750
and find a place for him to rest.

737
00:31:11,750 --> 00:31:13,410
Let me know when it's his turn.

738
00:31:15,510 --> 00:31:16,680
Hello, this way please.

739
00:31:16,680 --> 00:31:18,080
Let me carry this for you.

740
00:31:20,310 --> 00:31:22,440
This woman loves showing off too much.

741
00:31:23,160 --> 00:31:24,310
Ungrateful.

742
00:31:25,400 --> 00:31:26,540
Are you the manager?

743
00:31:26,690 --> 00:31:27,550
How can I help you?

744
00:31:27,550 --> 00:31:28,480
Could you please check

745
00:31:28,480 --> 00:31:30,480
if my room faces the sun?

746
00:31:30,960 --> 00:31:31,750
Luo Qingping,

747
00:31:31,750 --> 00:31:32,790
please take this gentleman

748
00:31:32,790 --> 00:31:34,680
to the executive floor,
find him an empty room,

749
00:31:34,680 --> 00:31:36,110
and send me the room number.

750
00:31:36,110 --> 00:31:36,680
Okay.

751
00:31:36,920 --> 00:31:37,960
-You can follow her.
-This way, please.

752
00:31:37,960 --> 00:31:38,960
Okay, thank you.

753
00:31:38,960 --> 00:31:39,890
You're welcome.

754
00:31:39,960 --> 00:31:40,720
Let me check for you.

755
00:31:40,720 --> 00:31:42,790
Okay. I have rheumatism in my legs.

756
00:31:42,790 --> 00:31:43,790
My doctor says I need

757
00:31:43,790 --> 00:31:45,000
to get sunlight every day.

758
00:31:45,000 --> 00:31:47,460
So I'd like to switch
to a south-facing room.

759
00:31:47,920 --> 00:31:49,310
Do you remember which receptionist

760
00:31:49,310 --> 00:31:50,170
checked you in?

761
00:31:50,240 --> 00:31:51,640
The one in the middle.

762
00:31:51,640 --> 00:31:52,370
Right there.

763
00:31:53,640 --> 00:31:54,960
Okay, give this to me.

764
00:31:54,960 --> 00:31:55,920
Please wait a moment.

765
00:31:55,920 --> 00:31:56,550
Okay.

766
00:31:57,110 --> 00:31:58,040
Enjoy your stay.

767
00:31:58,160 --> 00:31:58,880
Thank you.

768
00:31:59,000 --> 00:31:59,680
Xiaoyan.

769
00:31:59,680 --> 00:32:00,880
Why is it you again?

770
00:32:01,310 --> 00:32:02,550
Could you help this lady

771
00:32:02,550 --> 00:32:03,640
switch to a south-facing room?

772
00:32:03,640 --> 00:32:04,940
Go find someone else.

773
00:32:05,000 --> 00:32:06,800
These computers are connected.

774
00:32:07,240 --> 00:32:08,440
You're so fast.

775
00:32:08,440 --> 00:32:09,720
It'd be easy for you to switch it.

776
00:32:09,720 --> 00:32:10,510
I'm fast,

777
00:32:10,510 --> 00:32:11,960
but it's not to clean up your mess.

778
00:32:11,960 --> 00:32:12,640
If you don't know the job,

779
00:32:12,640 --> 00:32:14,270
don't play the hero here.

780
00:32:15,270 --> 00:32:16,930
Hello, please show me your ID.

781
00:32:18,030 --> 00:32:20,090
Please give me a corner room.

782
00:32:20,310 --> 00:32:21,480
I don't sleep well,

783
00:32:21,750 --> 00:32:23,010
so I want it to be quiet.

784
00:32:24,720 --> 00:32:26,030
I'm sorry, sir.

785
00:32:26,030 --> 00:32:28,720
We don't have a room
that meets your needs right now.

786
00:32:28,720 --> 00:32:30,480
You could try swapping

787
00:32:30,480 --> 00:32:32,750
with another alumnus after you check in.

788
00:32:32,750 --> 00:32:33,550
Wait a moment.

789
00:32:34,960 --> 00:32:37,580
Excuse me, may I see your room card?

790
00:32:40,540 --> 00:32:41,960
I might have a guest here

791
00:32:41,960 --> 00:32:43,510
who can swap rooms with you.

792
00:32:44,000 --> 00:32:44,960
Okay.

793
00:32:47,660 --> 00:32:48,970
Please follow me.

794
00:32:53,110 --> 00:32:54,940
Your rooms have been swapped.

795
00:32:55,000 --> 00:32:56,720
This one,

796
00:32:56,720 --> 00:32:58,750
1119, is facing the sun.

797
00:32:58,750 --> 00:33:00,310
This one, 1126, is a corner room.

798
00:33:00,310 --> 00:33:01,510
You can go upstairs to rest.

799
00:33:01,510 --> 00:33:03,790
I'll go over there
and swap your information.

800
00:33:03,790 --> 00:33:04,880
Okay.

801
00:33:07,510 --> 00:33:08,240
Xiaoyan,

802
00:33:08,240 --> 00:33:09,240
please swap the guest information

803
00:33:09,240 --> 00:33:10,440
for rooms 1119

804
00:33:10,440 --> 00:33:11,720
and 1126.

805
00:33:12,720 --> 00:33:13,240
Got it.

806
00:33:13,480 --> 00:33:15,030
Tell them to come over
for facial recognition.

807
00:33:15,030 --> 00:33:15,720
Okay.

808
00:33:18,030 --> 00:33:19,330
Attention, everyone.

809
00:33:19,480 --> 00:33:21,400
When I call your name,

810
00:33:21,400 --> 00:33:22,750
please come over here

811
00:33:22,750 --> 00:33:25,270
to take a photo
and get your passport and room card.

812
00:33:25,270 --> 00:33:27,510
First, Mr. Zhang Mingyuan.

813
00:33:28,270 --> 00:33:29,330
Wait here a moment.

814
00:33:30,100 --> 00:33:31,310
Ms. Wen Yan.

815
00:33:31,310 --> 00:33:32,980
Mr. Wang Zhifan.

816
00:33:33,270 --> 00:33:34,780
Mr. Ma Zhendong.

817
00:33:35,000 --> 00:33:36,480
Okay, please follow me

818
00:33:36,480 --> 00:33:38,270
to do facial recognition here.

819
00:33:38,270 --> 00:33:40,720
Hello, could you tell me
where the elevator is?

820
00:33:40,720 --> 00:33:42,120
The elevator is this way.

821
00:33:42,960 --> 00:33:44,960
Okay. Please come and register too.

822
00:33:46,640 --> 00:33:49,010
Hello, where's the restroom?

823
00:33:49,480 --> 00:33:51,110
There's one this way,

824
00:33:51,110 --> 00:33:51,720
and also one over there.

825
00:33:51,720 --> 00:33:52,900
Both ones will do.

826
00:33:53,310 --> 00:33:55,330
Why was the information desk
moved here?

827
00:33:55,330 --> 00:33:57,160
Ms. Xu asked me to move it.

828
00:33:57,160 --> 00:33:58,790
She said there are a lot of guests today,

829
00:33:58,790 --> 00:34:00,030
most of them elderly,

830
00:34:00,030 --> 00:34:01,270
and they have trouble walking.

831
00:34:01,270 --> 00:34:02,680
Moving it here makes it easier for them,

832
00:34:02,680 --> 00:34:04,720
and we can also help out the reception.

833
00:34:04,720 --> 00:34:05,100
Okay.

834
00:34:06,240 --> 00:34:06,840
Hello.

835
00:34:07,000 --> 00:34:08,710
Two of us have officially checked in.

836
00:34:08,710 --> 00:34:10,710
I was wondering if...

837
00:34:11,280 --> 00:34:12,880
Xu Miyu? Is Xu Miyu here?

838
00:34:12,880 --> 00:34:13,440
Here.

839
00:34:13,510 --> 00:34:14,110
Okay.

840
00:34:14,179 --> 00:34:15,280
You're delivering medicine, right?

841
00:34:15,280 --> 00:34:16,110
Okay, thanks.

842
00:34:16,320 --> 00:34:17,580
What kind of medicine?

843
00:34:18,000 --> 00:34:18,800
I don't know.

844
00:34:18,800 --> 00:34:19,969
Ms. Xu ordered it.

845
00:34:20,030 --> 00:34:21,670
I'll ask her to come get it now.

846
00:34:21,670 --> 00:34:23,190
I'll take it to her. It's on my way.

847
00:34:23,190 --> 00:34:23,630
Okay.

848
00:34:38,320 --> 00:34:39,000
Mr. Ji.

849
00:34:39,510 --> 00:34:41,040
Is there anything you need?

850
00:34:41,710 --> 00:34:43,480
Just checking in on the elderly

851
00:34:43,480 --> 00:34:44,400
guests.

852
00:34:50,040 --> 00:34:52,320
How's your new room?

853
00:34:53,150 --> 00:34:55,210
It's only for a few days. I can make do.

854
00:34:57,070 --> 00:34:58,110
Once the event is over,

855
00:34:58,110 --> 00:34:58,970
I'll move back.

856
00:35:01,190 --> 00:35:03,320
So you moved rooms to make space
for the Lusia University

857
00:35:03,320 --> 00:35:04,550
Alumni Association?

858
00:35:04,880 --> 00:35:05,710
What else?

859
00:35:06,820 --> 00:35:07,550
Makes sense.

860
00:35:13,150 --> 00:35:14,400
[Rest early after taking the medicine.]

861
00:35:13,670 --> 00:35:15,470
Your delivery from downstairs.

862
00:35:16,410 --> 00:35:17,040
Thank you.

863
00:35:31,280 --> 00:35:32,550
Are you feeling okay?

864
00:35:34,480 --> 00:35:36,280
I-I bought medicine for a guest.

865
00:35:40,190 --> 00:35:41,030
It's fine.

866
00:35:51,350 --> 00:35:56,530
[Lusia University Alumni Association
Anniversary Reunion]

867
00:35:52,110 --> 00:35:53,190
Finally done.

868
00:35:53,190 --> 00:35:54,150
I'm exhausted.

869
00:35:54,280 --> 00:35:55,190
I'm so hungry.

870
00:35:56,590 --> 00:35:57,710
Let's go eat.

871
00:35:56,630 --> 00:36:01,060
[Purong Hotel]

872
00:35:58,320 --> 00:35:59,510
Let's go eat!

873
00:36:00,070 --> 00:36:00,600
Good job.

874
00:36:00,670 --> 00:36:01,360
Good job.

875
00:36:10,600 --> 00:36:11,530
Thank you.

876
00:36:17,920 --> 00:36:19,280
What are you guys eating?

877
00:36:19,280 --> 00:36:21,440
Director Bai, what took you so long?

878
00:36:21,440 --> 00:36:23,700
His daughter is sick. Haven't you heard?

879
00:36:25,710 --> 00:36:27,590
Director Bai, how's your daughter?

880
00:36:27,590 --> 00:36:28,710
Has her fever gone down?

881
00:36:28,710 --> 00:36:30,030
She finished her checkup and went home.

882
00:36:30,030 --> 00:36:32,830
Fortunately, it's not
mycoplasma or adenovirus.

883
00:36:33,510 --> 00:36:35,590
You must have been so worried
about your daughter.

884
00:36:35,590 --> 00:36:37,320
It would be a lie to say I wasn't.

885
00:36:39,510 --> 00:36:40,710
But while I was in the hospital,

886
00:36:40,710 --> 00:36:42,440
I kept thinking about you guys.

887
00:36:42,510 --> 00:36:44,590
Over 100 people checking in at once,

888
00:36:44,590 --> 00:36:46,150
most of them elderly.

889
00:36:47,190 --> 00:36:48,550
You've all worked hard.

890
00:36:48,550 --> 00:36:49,840
You did a great job today.

891
00:36:49,840 --> 00:36:51,370
Everything went smoothly.

892
00:36:52,280 --> 00:36:53,080
I'm starving.

893
00:36:54,800 --> 00:36:56,260
Why is there only one left?

894
00:36:59,030 --> 00:37:00,840
Did I take someone's meal?

895
00:37:00,860 --> 00:37:02,900
What are you talking about?

896
00:37:03,230 --> 00:37:04,280
You're our leader.

897
00:37:04,280 --> 00:37:06,340
Of course there's a box lunch for you.

898
00:37:07,030 --> 00:37:08,230
Sorry, Ms. Xu.

899
00:37:08,400 --> 00:37:09,710
We didn't get enough box lunches.

900
00:37:09,710 --> 00:37:12,370
Go to the cafeteria
and see if there are any left.

901
00:37:14,110 --> 00:37:15,210
I feel so bad.

902
00:37:15,400 --> 00:37:17,330
How about I order you some takeout?

903
00:37:17,400 --> 00:37:18,190
No need.

904
00:37:19,070 --> 00:37:19,930
I'm not hungry.

905
00:37:22,030 --> 00:37:24,110
Ms. Xu, you can have mine.

906
00:37:24,110 --> 00:37:25,440
You've been busy all day.

907
00:37:25,440 --> 00:37:26,840
It's fine. You eat it.

908
00:37:30,710 --> 00:37:31,710
Hurry up and eat.

909
00:37:34,920 --> 00:37:35,880
Eat more.

910
00:37:41,510 --> 00:37:42,320
Mr. Ji.

911
00:37:44,320 --> 00:37:45,510
You haven't had dinner yet, have you?

912
00:37:45,510 --> 00:37:46,070
Here.

913
00:37:48,190 --> 00:37:49,070
I have food.

914
00:37:51,080 --> 00:37:53,190
I accidentally ordered extra.

915
00:37:53,190 --> 00:37:54,720
It'd be a waste not to eat it.

916
00:37:56,400 --> 00:37:57,070
Thank you.

917
00:37:59,110 --> 00:38:00,370
Take care of yourself.

918
00:38:02,250 --> 00:38:03,100
Ms. Xu,

919
00:38:03,440 --> 00:38:05,100
Room 1801 is looking for you.

920
00:38:06,800 --> 00:38:07,670
Copy...

921
00:38:08,280 --> 00:38:09,150
Eat first.

922
00:38:10,800 --> 00:38:12,590
Yin Xiang, go to Room 1801.

923
00:38:13,650 --> 00:38:14,570
Copy that.

924
00:39:00,180 --> 00:39:03,270
[Purong Hotel]

925
00:39:14,320 --> 00:39:15,550
Starting tomorrow,

926
00:39:15,550 --> 00:39:17,190
the lobby will be short a manager.

927
00:39:17,190 --> 00:39:18,440
If you don't decide soon,

928
00:39:18,440 --> 00:39:20,440
Bai Yongjun will come crying to you.

929
00:39:22,280 --> 00:39:23,320
What do you think of her?

930
00:39:22,420 --> 00:39:24,510
[Employee Internal Promotion
Application Form]

931
00:39:27,150 --> 00:39:28,150
What do you think?

932
00:39:28,320 --> 00:39:29,880
I think her abilities are average.

933
00:39:29,880 --> 00:39:32,400
She has some authority among those

934
00:39:32,400 --> 00:39:33,660
young receptionists,

935
00:39:34,070 --> 00:39:35,920
but when it comes to
professional and leadership skills,

936
00:39:35,920 --> 00:39:37,710
she's definitely not qualified.

937
00:39:37,710 --> 00:39:39,280
If Xu Miyu hadn't

938
00:39:39,280 --> 00:39:41,190
been backing her up
with the elderly group today,

939
00:39:41,190 --> 00:39:43,400
she couldn't have handled it on her own.

940
00:39:45,880 --> 00:39:47,460
Do you have any other candidates in mind?

941
00:39:47,460 --> 00:39:52,200
[Purong Hotel]

942
00:39:48,550 --> 00:39:49,710
If we want to be fair,

943
00:39:49,850 --> 00:39:52,330
external recruitment would be the fairest.

944
00:39:52,710 --> 00:39:54,570
But we simply don't have the time.

945
00:39:54,840 --> 00:39:57,420
Maybe we should just go with Lu Xiaoyan.

946
00:39:57,550 --> 00:39:58,840
Consider it a favor to Bai Yongjun.

947
00:39:58,840 --> 00:40:01,370
After all, she's
his strong recommendation.

948
00:40:04,150 --> 00:40:05,680
Do you have someone in mind?

949
00:40:09,800 --> 00:40:10,860
Take a look at this.

950
00:40:12,440 --> 00:40:15,480
[Career Direction Assessment Report]

951
00:40:12,760 --> 00:40:15,700
This person's assessment data
is quite impressive.

952
00:40:15,920 --> 00:40:17,670
A natural for the hotel industry.

953
00:40:17,670 --> 00:40:18,550
Bound to go far.

954
00:40:19,550 --> 00:40:20,320
Who's this?

955
00:40:21,510 --> 00:40:22,280
Xu Miyu.
